              Our multi-sensor fusion platform for biomechanics analysis. See it in action with real research data.
            </p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Signal, not noise -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="bg-white/[0.02] p-10 rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.04]">
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Northlake Labs is a biomechanics and AI company founded by 
            <a href="/about/" class="text-burnt-sienna hover:text-burnt-sienna/80 transition-colors">Geoffrey Brown</a>, 
